subMembers.name: Configuration
subMembers.description: This section describes properties that configure the **XmlaStore**.

subMembers.name: beforeSend
subMembers.description: Specifies a function that customizes the request before it is sent to the server.

subMembers.name: catalog
subMembers.description: Specifies the database (or initial catalog) that contains the OLAP cube to use.

subMembers.name: cube
subMembers.description: Specifies the name of the OLAP cube to use from the [catalog].

properties.name: XmlaStore
properties.description: The **XmlaStore** is a store that provides an interface for accessing an OLAP cube according to the XMLA standard.
